						<summary>

						<p>This inscription seems to record some gift to the temple of Śri Pōndai-Āṇdār at Rājamallach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam of Tiruvēgambapuram in Dāmark-kōṭṭam. This gift was left in charge of the <hi rend="italic">gaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> who looked after the temple administration [<hi rend="italic">śrī kāryam</hi>].</p>						

						</summary>
